query:
SELECT s.id, s.title, se.setNumber, se.position, se.notes 
FROM songs s 
JOIN setlist_entries se ON s.id = se.songId 
JOIN concerts c ON se.concertId = c.id 
WHERE c.id = 60001 
ORDER BY se.setNumber, se.position 
LIMIT 10
